{{Use dmy dates|date=September 2014}} {{Infobox person | name = Martina Montelius | image = Martina Montelius.jpg | caption = Martina Montelius (2013) | birth_date ={{Birth date and age|1975|7|19|df=y}} | birth_place = [[Stockholm]], Sweden | occupation = [[Author]] | known_for = | height = }}
'''Martina Montelius''' (born 19 July 1975) is a [[Swedes|Swedish]] author, director and playwright. She has written several plays, has had three novels published and also worked as an artistic director.
==Career== Montelius grew up in [[Täby]], Sweden and went to school at the Eriksdalsschool.<ref name="Ger fingret åt det fina">{{cite web |url=http://www.fokus.se/2013/10/ger-fingret-at-det-fina/ |title=Ger fingret åt det fina |deadurl=no |accessdate=2 September 2014}}</ref> During her teenage years, she worked at a library at [[Medborgarplatsen]] and later worked for the [[Dramaten]] and Teater Plaza.<ref>{{cite web|quote=Does not display on Chrome browser. |url=http://www.svd.se/bostad/odramatiskt-i-vallingby_2969265.svd |title=Odramatiskt i Vällingby - Bostad - SvD |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2 September 2014 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121018074023/http://www.svd.se/bostad/odramatiskt-i-vallingby_2969265.svd |archivedate=18 October 2012 }}</ref><ref name="Dominika Peczyski & Martina Montelius">{{cite web |url=http://pasparetbloggen.blogspot.se/2013/11/dominika-peczyski-martina-montelius.html |title=Dominika Peczyski & Martina Montelius |deadurl=no |accessdate=2 September 2014}}</ref> At Plaza she started a long co-operation with actor and director [[Thorsten Flinck]].<ref name="Favoritpar och nypåstigna tävlade i På spåret">{{cite web |url=http://www.svt.se/pa-sparet/de-tavlar-i-pa-sparet-i-host |title=Favoritpar och nypåstigna tävlade i På spåret |deadurl=no|publisher=svt.se|accessdate=2 September 2014}}</ref> She was a director and actress for his shows before starting to write her own work.<ref name="Favoritpar och nypåstigna tävlade i På spåret"/>
In 2000, she made her debut as a playwright with the play ''Usch, nu blev jag lite mulen'', and has since written fifteen more plays.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://sverigesradio.se/sida/avsnitt/400239?programid=2071 |title=Martina Montelius |deadurl=no|publisher=sverigesradio.se |accessdate=2 September 2014}}</ref> In 2011 she was appointed artistic director for the Teater Brunnsgatan Fyra Theater, a job she took over from her mother.<ref name="Ger fingret åt det fina"/> In November 2013 she had her first book published, ''Främlingsleguanen'', which was published by Bokförlaget Atlas.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.svd.se/kultur/litteratur/en-hemsk-och-ljuvlig-debutroman_8694624.svd |title=En hemsk och ljuvlig debutroman |deadurl=no |publisher=svd.se |accessdate=2 September 2014}}</ref>
==In popular culture== In 2013, Montelius was a contestant on ''[[På spåret]]'' at [[Sveriges Television|SVT]] along with [[Dominika Peczynski]].<ref name="Dominika Peczyski & Martina Montelius"/> She hosted her own episode of the popular Swedish talk radio show ''[[Sommar i P1]]'' in summer 2014. Her episode was broadcast live while most ''Sommar i P1'' episodes are pre-recorded and then aired.<ref name="MonteliusSvD">{{cite web |url=http://www.svd.se/kultur/sommar-i-p1-martina-montelius_3760530.svd|title=Ett yvigt kontrollerat vansinne|deadurl=no|publisher=svd.se |accessdate=6 September 2014}}</ref> Her episode was reviewed by ''[[Svenska Dagbladet]]'', who described it as "controlled madness and seductive".<ref name="MonteliusSvD1">{{cite web|url=http://www.svd.se/kultur/sommar-i-p1-martina-montelius_3760530.svd |title=Ett yvigt kontrollerat vansinne |deadurl=yes |accessdate=6 September 2014 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141011130633/http://www.svd.se/kultur/sommar-i-p1-martina-montelius_3760530.svd |archivedate=11 October 2014 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aftonbladet.se/nyheter/article19242559.ab|title=Berättarglädje som slår fartrekord - Nyheter - Aftonbladet|work=Aftonbladet|accessdate=13 September 2014}}</ref>
==Personal life== Montelius is the daughter of the poet and dramatist [[Kristina Lugn]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sydsvenskan.se/kultur--nojen/bocker/bokrecensioner/ingen-ar-som-mamma/ |title=Ingen är som mamma |deadurl=no|publisher=sydsvenskan.se |accessdate=2 September 2014}}</ref> She has three children with her husband. Montelius has said that she grew up in an artistic family and that she herself now is looking for the regular family life.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dn.se/kultur-noje/martina-montelius-det-kravs-sa-lite-for-att-sticka-ut/ |title=Martina Montelius: "Det krävs så lite för att sticka ut" |deadurl=no|publisher=dn.se |accessdate=6 September 2014}}</ref>
